leader i will reformat you all. You will become TechenOrganic A perfect 
balance of Technology and Organic. that is how The matrix intended us to be 
so that is how we will."

:::He raised his hands and focused energy. Every fiber in his body quivered 
and began to change. He started becoming a TechnOrganic he grew and changed 
colour. His Wings Flourished and His Power grew. He passed his Hands over 
Herald, Tran, Talin, Data, Defection. They all became TechenOrganic with new 
bodies and more power. Then he stopped his hands and spoke to Gigatron and 
the SkySchorchers:::

Child; "Because I have no relation to you all I need your permission to make
